    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches expected from normal driving, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major stains or tears. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, shifts well, and all major electronics are fully functional. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that has plenty of life left in it.",
