    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to fall in love with this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving exactly like the day it left the showroom. It has been meticulously maintained and cared for, presenting a rare opportunity to own a car that is practically flawless inside and out.",
