    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and long-term value. Maintained to rigorous standards, the exterior retains its original luster while the interior reflects conscientious ownership. Mechanically sound and thoroughly inspected, this unit offers a dependable driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the integrity of this well-preserved automobile.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
