      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is super reliable and totally ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, and it still drives like a dream. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical highlights include a documented Double VANOS overhaul and a proactively reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary stress points. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, providing predictable lock-up during spirited cornering. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are strong, with linear power delivery through the 8,000 RPM redline and a firm, communicative suspension feel. A well-sorted example of BMW's ultimate analog M-car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW M3 is a striking example of modern performance, finished in a deep Mineral Grey Metallic that has retained its lustrous shine. As a detail-oriented owner, I\u2019ve ensured the car remains in impressive shape; while there are a few minor rock chips on the front hood and a light scuff on one of the 19-inch M-Double Spoke wheels, the body lines are crisp and free of any dents. The interior is a sanctuary of Black Extended Merino leather, which has been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking, showing only soft creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every technological feature, including the iDrive navigation and the premium Harman Kardon audio system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the twin-turbo inline-six runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service log and a recent professional inspection that confirms the cooling system and gaskets are in excellent health. It\u2019s a turn-key enthusiast car that balances raw power with the refined comfort of a well-kept daily driver.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both engineering integrity and sustained performance. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical reliability and interior preservation. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and robust capabilities, this represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning professional seeking a balance of luxury and utility. Invest in a vehicle that commands respect on the road without compromise.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    }
